description: Lion Rock Resources Inc. engages in acquiring, exploring, developing, and evaluating mineral resource properties in Canada. It focuses on the Maybrun property, a gold-copper project located approximately 80 km southeast of Kenora, Ontario. The company was formerly known as King's Bay Resources Corp. and changed its name to Lion Rock Resources Inc. in July 2022. Lion Rock Resources Inc. was incorporated in 1998 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
ceo: Mr. R. Dale Ginn B.Sc., P.Geo., P.Geol.
